list_definition_mean.definition: to (cause to) grow in size, number etc
ex_of_definition_list: The number of children in this school has increased greatly in recent years.

list_definition_mean.definition: (the amount, number etc added by) growth

list_definition_mean.definition: an increase especially in salary

list_definition_mean.definition: to begin (a line of writing) farther in from the margin than the other lines
ex_of_definition_list: You should indent the first line of each new paragraph.

list_definition_mean.definition: an alphabetical list of names, subjects etc eg at the end of a book
ex_of_definition_list: Look it up in the index.

list_definition_mean.definition: a pointer, sign, instrument etc which indicates something or gives information about something
ex_of_definition_list: the indicator on the petrol gauge of a car.

list_definition_mean.definition: the qualities that distinguish one person etc from others
ex_of_definition_list: Teachers must take account of the individuality of each student.

list_definition_mean.definition: single; separate

list_definition_mean.definition: intended for, used by etc one person etc

list_definition_mean.definition: special to one person etc, showing or having special qualities

list_definition_mean.definition: a single person in contrast to the group to which he belongs
ex_of_definition_list: the rights of the individual in society.

list_definition_mean.definition: a person

list_definition_mean.definition: used, done etc inside a building

an indoor swimming-pool.

list_definition_mean.definition: having, concerning etc industries or the making of goods

list_definition_mean.definition: hard work or effort

list_definition_mean.definition: (the part of an army consisting of) foot-soldiers

list_definition_mean.definition: a baby or very young child

(also adjective) an infant school.

list_definition_mean.definition: a disease

list_definition_mean.definition: likely to spread to others

list_definition_mean.definition: without end or limits

list_definition_mean.definition: very great

list_definition_mean.definition: in mathematics, an indefinitely large number, quantity or distance

list_definition_mean.definition: easily set on fire

list_definition_mean.definition: (a place in the body where there is) development of heat with pain, redness and swelling

list_definition_mean.definition: (of eg a cushion, ball etc) that can be filled with air for use

list_definition_mean.definition: to blow up or expand (especially a balloon, tyre or lungs with air)

list_definition_mean.definition: a situation in country’s economy where prices and wages keep forcing each other to increase

list_definition_mean.definition: to have an effect on

list_definition_mean.definition: a type of infectious illness usually causing headache, fever, a cold etc
ex_of_definition_list: The drug is highly effective at preventing influenza.

list_definition_mean.definition: someone who tells or informs

list_definition_mean.definition: giving useful information
ex_of_definition_list: an informative book.

list_definition_mean.definition: a mass of metal (eg gold or silver) cast in a mould/mold

list_definition_mean.definition: one of the things that go into a mixture

list_definition_mean.definition: a black or coloured/colored liquid used in writing, printing etc

list_definition_mean.definition: (of feelings etc) secret or hidden

list_definition_mean.definition: (the act of making) a change or a new arrangement etc

list_definition_mean.definition: not having the special characteristics of living bodies; not organic

list_definition_mean.definition: something written, eg on a gravestone or on a coin

list_definition_mean.definition: unsure of oneself or lacking confidence

list_definition_mean.definition: the stomach and bowels

list_definition_mean.definition: being on or in the inside

list_definition_mean.definition: to, in, or on, the inside

list_definition_mean.definition: in a house or building

list_definition_mean.definition: (sometimes especially American with of) within; to or on the inside of

list_definition_mean.definition: (sometimes with of) in less than, or within, a certain time
ex_of_definition_list: He finished the work inside (of) two days.

list_definition_mean.definition: (the quality of having) an understanding of something
ex_of_definition_list: He shows remarkable insight (into children’s problems).

list_definition_mean.definition: symbols worn or carried as a mark of high office

list_definition_mean.definition: not having enough money to pay your debts; bankrupt

list_definition_mean.definition: inability to sleep

list_definition_mean.definition: a person appointed to inspect
ex_of_definition_list: a school inspector.
